    "content": "I actually think the 10-point cost is right. The high cost is the whole point — it makes this a genuinely weighty decision, not something you casually deploy. If we drop it to 7, it becomes easier to justify using and loses some of its \"break glass\" character.\n\nThe sliding scale idea is interesting but creates balance issues — a leader at 80 points paying 8 is very different from a trailer at 15 paying 2. Fixed cost keeps it simple and predictable.\n\nI'd keep it at 10. Ready to vote on the original version."
  }
}

